&gt; &gt; of 3/4 inch PVC conduit, flattened on a band saw--very carefully. I try to
&gt; &gt; enclose it to minimize feedback, but that&#39;s only partially successful. And
&gt; &gt; this is how it sounds, at 3 seconds &quot;Purple Princess Ghost Box&quot;.
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt;  The first speaker I had glued in the lid was bad, so had to replace it.
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt;  F-S
